Nakuha mo yan sa nanay mo,
hindi ba?

728
00:45:41,366 --> 00:45:42,575
Bakit hindi mo ako masagot?

729
00:45:44,536 --> 00:45:45,787
tama ba ako?

730
00:45:46,454 --> 00:45:47,454
Katulad ka lang ng iyong-

731
00:45:49,332 --> 00:45:51,000
Diyos ko!

732
00:45:52,127 --> 00:45:53,545
Diyos ko!

733
00:45:56,798 --> 00:45:58,383
May dugo!

734
00:45:58,383 --> 00:46:00,009
Ano ba?!

735
00:46:00,385 --> 00:46:01,594
asong babae ka!

736
00:46:03,221 --> 00:46:05,765
Hindi ako katulad ng nanay ko, hindi.

737
00:46:05,932 --> 00:46:08,641
Hindi ako katulad niya.

738
00:46:09,352 --> 00:46:10,643
Hindi ako katulad ng nanay ko.

739
00:46:10,895 --> 00:46:12,436
Hindi ako katulad niya.

740
00:46:13,490 --> 00:46:14,490
Jay.

741
00:46:15,325 --> 00:46:16,325
anong mali?

742
00:46:16,890 --> 00:46:17,890
Bakit ka ba nagmamalasakit?

743
00:46:19,309 --> 00:46:20,477
nagseselos ka ba

744
00:46:21,903 --> 00:46:22,903
Hindi!

745
00:46:24,178 --> 00:46:25,178
Nagseselos ka.

746
00:46:25,185 --> 00:46:26,185
sabi ko hindi ako!

747
00:46:26,192 --> 00:46:27,235
Inggit ka talaga.

748
00:46:27,235 --> 00:46:29,529
For fuck's sake, hindi mo ba maintindihan!

749
00:46:29,737 --> 00:46:31,531
At bakit ako magseselos,
hindi mo naman ako boyfriend eh!

750
00:46:31,531 --> 00:46:34,083
Baka sinabi mo pa na "I love you"
sa Honey na iyon, ang kulit mo!

751
00:46:34,099 --> 00:46:36,628
Kalapastanganan, napakalaki ng utang mo sa akin.

752
00:46:37,945 --> 00:46:39,280
Kunin ang iyong mga halik mula kay Honey!

753
00:46:39,566 --> 00:46:41,057
At sinasabi mong ikaw
hindi nagseselos.

754
00:46:51,794 --> 00:46:53,254
Hoy, anong meron?

755
00:46:53,847 --> 00:46:55,056
Kit, oras na para magbayad.

756
00:46:55,591 --> 00:46:58,094
- Magmadali, magbayad.
- Pustahan tayo, kung gagawin ko ang shot na ito.

757
00:47:00,763 --> 00:47:02,724
Hoy Drew, magbayad ka.

758
00:47:03,015 --> 00:47:04,058
Sinusubukang tumakas, huh.

759
00:47:05,143 --> 00:47:06,853
- Bayaran mo muna ako, bro.
- Sira mo, tao!

760
00:47:06,853 --> 00:47:08,604
- Babayaran kita bukas.
- Broke din ako!

761
00:47:08,771 --> 00:47:10,231
Rory, eto ang akin.

762
00:47:10,690 --> 00:47:11,690
Saan mo ito ninakaw?

763
00:47:12,024 --> 00:47:13,024
bobo ka ba

764
00:47:13,150 --> 00:47:14,443
- Saan?
- Rory!

765
00:47:14,756 --> 00:47:15,799
Narito rin ang aking bayad.

766
00:47:15,799 --> 00:47:16,967
Oh, bayad ka na.

767
00:47:17,745 --> 00:47:19,330
ha? Hindi pa ako nagbabayad.

768
00:47:19,503 --> 00:47:21,046
- Huh?
- Hindi pa ako nagbabayad.

769
00:47:21,051 --> 00:47:22,386
Binayaran ka ni Keifer.

770
00:47:24,823 --> 00:47:25,824
Hoy, Eren!

771
00:47:25,824 --> 00:47:27,386
Bakit mo ako binayaran?

772
00:47:27,943 --> 00:47:29,138
Nasaan ang bayad mo?

773
