gusto ko.

774
00:47:34,032 --> 00:47:35,227
Pero iyon ang gastos ko.

775
00:47:36,827 --> 00:47:38,021
Ano ang mali dito?

776
00:47:38,328 --> 00:47:40,120
Ginamot na kita dati, remember?

777
00:47:41,206 --> 00:47:42,206
Kahit ano,

778
00:47:42,541 --> 00:47:44,209
Babayaran ko ang sarili kong gastusin.

779
00:47:46,628 --> 00:47:49,590
Bakit hindi ka sumasagot
mga tawag ko kagabi?

780
00:47:50,102 --> 00:47:51,102
hindi ko alam.

781
00:47:51,127 --> 00:47:52,537
Tanungin mo si Honey, baka alam niya.

782
00:47:54,564 --> 00:47:55,898
Nagseselos ka pa ba?

783
00:47:56,421 --> 00:47:57,798
Ako, nagseselos?

784
00:47:57,798 --> 00:47:58,924
Huh, sino ka pa rin?

785
00:48:01,510 --> 00:48:03,971
Alam mong gustong kasuhan ka ni Honey
dahil sa ginawa mo.

786
00:48:03,971 --> 00:48:05,264
Deserve niya ito.

787
00:48:06,473 --> 00:48:10,096
Magandang bagay
Kinumbinsi ko siyang huwag.

788
00:48:11,603 --> 00:48:14,058
Huh, hinalikan mo siya di ba?

789
00:48:17,150 --> 00:48:18,730
Magtiwala ka sa akin.

790
00:48:19,194 --> 00:48:22,608
Wala kang dahilan para magselos.

791
00:48:26,910 --> 00:48:28,156
Tandaan,

792
00:48:31,164 --> 00:48:32,164
ako sayo.

793
00:48:35,412 --> 00:48:36,412
Tatlo.

794
00:48:36,419 --> 00:48:37,420
Dalawa.

795
00:48:37,420 --> 00:48:38,582
Isa.

796
00:48:39,506 --> 00:48:42,425
[Seksyon E cheering]

797
00:48:49,474 --> 00:48:52,227
- Bakit ka namumula?
- Bawal yan dito.

798
00:48:53,685 --> 00:48:55,698
- Ang iyong mukha ay nagiging pula.
- "Namumula," parang!

799
00:48:58,588 --> 00:48:59,588
Yuri.

800
00:49:06,372 --> 00:49:08,262
Pinapatawag ka
ang guidance office, si Jay.

801
00:49:08,287 --> 00:49:09,287
Ako?

802
00:49:09,312 --> 00:49:11,115
- Oo.
- Huh?

803
00:49:11,513 --> 00:49:12,513
Iyon ang sinabi nila.

804
00:49:35,579 --> 00:49:36,622
Magandang umaga po.

805
00:49:37,259 --> 00:49:39,151
- Umupo ka.
- Tinatawag mo ba ako, ma'am?

806
00:49:39,151 --> 00:49:40,602
Oo, tahan na.

807
00:49:45,774 --> 00:49:49,778
Kailangan mong kunin ang pirma ng
tagapayo ng dati mong paaralan.

808
00:49:50,570 --> 00:49:52,197
Sa dati kong school?

809
00:49:53,198 --> 00:49:54,198
Bakit?

810
00:49:54,532 --> 00:49:57,953
Ang mga tala na ibinigay nila sa amin
noon ay hindi kumpleto.

811
00:49:58,161 --> 00:50:01,915
Tinatawagan namin sila,
pero lagi nilang sinasabi,

812
00:50:01,915 --> 00:50:03,125
"Tatawagan ka namin."

813
00:50:05,210 --> 00:50:06,295
Aking mga tala?

814
00:50:10,256 --> 00:50:12,718
Ano ang mangyayari kung
Hindi ko sila pinipirmahan?

815
00:50:13,841 --> 00:50:14,841
Aba,

816
00:50:16,334 --> 00:50:17,544
hindi ka makakapagtapos.

817
00:50:20,392 --> 00:50:22,018
<i>Ayokong bumalik doon.</i>

818
00:50:22,644 --> 00:50:24,771
<i>Paano kung makasalubong ko si Cyrus?</i>

819
00:50:26,106 --> 00:50:28,525
Malamang ay hindi gaano
ng abala para sa iyo.

820
00:50:28,900 --> 00:50:31,403
Lalo na dahil sa iyong
ang retreat ay sa susunod na linggo.

821
00:50:32,070 --> 00:50:35,031
Ito ay gaganapin malapit
ang dati mong paaralan.

822
00:50:35,782 --> 00:50:37,660
sana makuha mo
ito ang pinirmahan noon.

823
00:50:38,284 --> 00:50:40,704
Ipapaalam ko lang
iyong tagapayo tungkol dito.

824
00:50:40,704 --> 00:50:42,747
Kaya papayag sila
umalis ka na, okay?

825
00:50:44,156 --> 00:50:45,156
Okay.

826
00:50:57,345 --> 00:50:59,557
Hanggang kailan mo balak
para lokohin, Jay, ha?

827
00:51:01,933 --> 00:51:03,560
Oo!

828
00:51:03,661 --> 00:51:04,661
Wow!

829
00:51:04,686 --> 00:51:07,063
Magbo-bonding kayong lahat
kay Jay na parang hindi

830
00:51:07,063 --> 00:51:10,984
[Seksyon E fighting]

831
00:51:14,612 --> 00:51:16,532
Anong nangyayari?!

832
00:51:17,574 --> 00:51:19,702
Ano ang nangyayari?
Bakit kayo nag-aaway?!

833
00:51:25,123 --> 00:51:27,083
So, walang magsasalita?

834
00:52:29,403 --> 00:52:30,403
Sabihin mo sa akin,

835
00:52:30,855 --> 00:52:32,690
ano ka
lahat ng pinag-aawayan?

836
00:52:32,816 --> 00:52:33,983
Sabihin mo na lang sa kanya!

837
00:52:33,983 --> 00:52:35,485
tumahimik ka! Tumigil ka na sa pakikialam!

838
00:52:35,510 --> 00:52:37,278
Damn it, gumagawa ka lang
mas mahirap para kay Ci-N.

839
00:52:37,278 --> 00:52:38,278
Ganda ng kwarto.

840
00:52:38,293 --> 00:52:39,336
Anong ginagawa mo dito?

841
00:52:39,336 --> 00:52:40,699
Kaya kayo ni Keifer
magkasama ngayon.

842
00:52:40,994 --> 00:52:41,994
Paano naman si Yuri?

843
00:52:43,413 --> 00:52:44,706
Hindi siya aasa.

844
00:52:45,457 --> 00:52:47,250
Kung hindi mo siya binibigyan ng pag-asa.

845
00:52:47,334 --> 00:52:49,086
Wow!

846
00:52:49,086 --> 00:52:50,754
Tingnan kung sino ang nagsasalita.

847
00:52:50,879 --> 00:52:52,005
Sino ang unang nanakit sa kanya, ha?

848
00:52:52,005 --> 00:52:53,131
Sa'yo ba talaga nanggaling?

849
00:52:53,131 --> 00:52:54,966
Camping! Camping!

850
00:52:55,064 --> 00:52:56,065
Ang kampo ay bato, baby!

851
00:52:56,273 --> 00:52:57,858
Section E, ikaw ba yan?

852
00:52:57,858 --> 00:53:00,482
[Seksyon E cheering]

853
00:53:00,507 --> 00:53:03,535
Mga lalaki, 3, 2, 1.

854
00:53:04,761 --> 00:53:05,761
Hoy, Sir!

855
00:53:05,804 --> 00:53:07,139
Jay-jay, ikaw ba yan?

856
00:53:07,139 --> 00:53:08,557
Naku, hologram lang ito.

857
00:53:08,557 --> 00:53:10,725
Boyfriend mo si Cyrus diba?

858
00:53:11,226 --> 00:53:12,686
Balik school na naman siya.

859
00:53:14,187 --> 00:53:16,189
At magandang tingnan
nandito ka, Jay-jay.

860
00:53:16,189 --> 00:53:17,357
Hoy huwag kang umalis,

861
00:53:17,357 --> 00:53:18,775
